column2: SELECT      TOP #      s.ra, s.dec,      s.z,        p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMag_z,   p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMagErr_z,   p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z,         e.lgm_tot_p5#, e.lgm_tot_p8#, e.lgm_tot_p1#   e.sfr_tot_p5#, e.sfr_tot_p8#, e.sfr_tot_p1#       FROM galSpecLine AS g        JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid     JOIN galSpecExtra AS e ON e.specobjid = g.specobjid     JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS p ON p.specobjid = g.specobjid  WHERE      s.zwarning       = #
